title: Move Over Drake & Wale, Fong Sai U Drops “F*ck Meek Mill” Diss: “He Left Twitter To Get On Instagram” [Audio]
text: Move Over Drake & Wale, Fong Sai U Drops “F*ck Meek Mill” Diss: “He Left Twitter To Get On Instagram” [Audio] Friday, 23 October 2015 (12 minutes ago) Maybach Music Group’s Meek Mill has more to worry about than tensions with Young Money’s Drake and labelmate Wale thanks to Washington , DC native Fong Sai U delivering his hard-hitting “F*ck Meek Mill” diss. Speaking up for Wale and tired of the social media rants, Fong goes at Meek with some unexpected daggers. Listen now! The post Move Over Drake & Wale, Fong Sai U Drops “F*ck Meek Mill” Diss: “He Left Twitter To Get On Instagram ” [Audio] appeared first on For The Best In Hip-Hop News - SOHH.com.
